00:47:15.881 --> 00:47:16.064
of your writing.

00:47:16.064 --> 00:47:16.980
GRETCHEN RUBIN: Oh,
well thank you.

00:47:16.980 --> 00:47:19.615
AUDIENCE: So obviously you've
done a ton of research, and

00:47:19.615 --> 00:47:22.637
experience, and growing over
the past several years.

00:47:22.637 --> 00:47:25.306
So what is the one thing you
wish you would have known five

00:47:25.306 --> 00:47:25.702
or ten years ago?

00:47:25.702 --> 00:47:28.736
Or one thing you'd go back and
tell your younger self that

00:47:28.736 --> 00:47:30.642
you think would have improved
your happiness?

00:47:30.642 --> 00:47:33.160
GRETCHEN RUBIN: So the question
is knowing what I

00:47:33.160 --> 00:47:36.440
